snippet.title: Diablo – Opening Cinematic
snippet.description:
To celebrate Diablo’s 20th Anniversary, we’re remembering the game that started it all.

Deep beneath the quiet town of Tristram, a great evil stirs…

The first game in the popular series of the same name, Diablo delivers a dark gothic fantasy world to explore with real-time combat and a random loot system that keeps players coming back again and again.
